Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:25.57,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}擦肩而过的话语深处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:31.43,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}禁锢着开启心灵的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.08,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}你是开启这锁的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:41.58,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只愿你能拯救那笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:47.21,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夏风的指引  带来变革的风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:51.90,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}将波长同步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:57.36,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如同浪漫故事般  善解人意的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.92,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也无处可寻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:06.46,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只能以蓝天为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:11.30,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此我们就能合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:16.66,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论是迷茫的泪水  还是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:23.10,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}都是能被真实所吸引之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:26.96,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那即是太过惹人怜爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:31.51,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}魔法的记忆
